17

A GRAND JUROR: Can I just ask which airport is ISM?
THE WITNESS: You know, I can in the next session, I would be happy to bring the airport codes.
A GRAND JUROR: Okay.
THE WITNESS: Obviously, we focused in on his times when he traveled into the Palm Beach County area and that would be PBIA or PBI, but I can certainly provide all the airport codes at our next session.
BY MS. VILLAFANA:
Q All right. Now throughout the Overt Acts portion where there are discussions of various Jane Does, there will be mentioned a telephone call.
So, for example, if you look at Page Ten, Paragraph 17, it says on or about April 23rd, 2004, [REDACTED] placed a telephone call to a telephone used by [REDACTED].
Do you see that?
A Yes.
Q And Special Agent [REDACTED] what is the evidence that we have related to the telephone calls that are mentioned in the Overt Acts?
